<comment type="function">
<text>Lyase that catalyzes the formation of isoprene from dimethylallyl diphosphate, but not from isopentenyl diphosphate or geranyl diphosphate.</text>
</comment>
<comment type="catalytic activity">
<reaction>
<text>dimethylallyl diphosphate = diphosphate + isoprene</text>
